          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "To customize the segmented control appearance you need to provide divider images to go between two unselected segments ("
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "leftSegmentState:UIControlStateNormal rightSegmentState:UIControlStateNormal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "), selected on the left and unselected on the right ("
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "leftSegmentState:UIControlStateSelected rightSegmentState:UIControlStateNormal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "), and unselected on the left and selected on the right ("
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "leftSegmentState:UIControlStateNormal rightSegmentState:UIControlStateSelected"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ")."
